        "code": { "language": "markdown", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "Filters scope to **HTTP access logs**. Click any log row to expand all structured fields (request_id, duration_ms, client_ip, …). For full click-to-filter field search, use **Open in Explore** (top right) → select Loki → enter `{job=\"spp-app\"} | json`.",
